deal.highlightsHtml: Gather your crew and enjoy 2 hours of bowling with included free shoe rental!
deal.pitchHtml:
Let the good times roll at Bowlero!

Step into a venue that feels less like your typical alley and more like a high-energy playground where unforgettable memories are made. Imagine sleek bowling lanes illuminated by black lights, plush lounge seating that invites you to kick back between turns, and HD video walls that amplify every strike and spare. Here, you can take your game to a whole new level!

What We Offer

  • Two Hours of Bowling for 2, 4, or 6 People, Includes Free Shoe Rental
    • Valid at Bowlero locations, listed here.
    • Includes free shoe rentals for each guest!
    • Each voucher good for one lane.
    • Please check Bowlero.com prior to your visit to check each center’s hours of operation.
    • Not valid until 24 hours after purchase.
    • Not valid on Saturdays after 6 PM.
    • Retail values vary by location.

Thrilling Lanes, Unmatched Entertainment, and Delicious Food


Get ready for hours of excitement! Bowl in an electrifying atmosphere featuring black lights, booming music, and massive HD video walls that keep the energy high. Whether you're perfecting your game or just out for fun, the lanes are waiting!

But that's not all—take a break from bowling to practice your trick shots with a game of billiards, suit up for an adrenaline-fueled laser tag, prepare yourself for the ultimate arcade experience, relax in the vintage lounge, or watch the big game on HD TVs with a drink in hand.

When hunger hits, their epic eats deliver—think towering nachos, juicy burgers, saucy wings, cheesy pizza, and signature sandwiches with bold twists. Cool down after a heated game with their delicious shareable drinks or creamy milkshakes!

Easy-to-Find Locations Nationwide

Bowlero has dozens of locations across the country. Wherever you are, a fun-packed experience is just around the corner. Check the valid locations for this voucher here.

You’re almost there! Follow these easy steps and then let the games begin!

  1. Grab Your Voucher: After you buy the Groupon offer, you’ll receive your voucher. Please note—the voucher is valid 24 hours after purchase and not available on Saturdays after 6 PM.
  2. Plan Your Visit: Check Bowlero.com for each location’s hours of operation prior to your visit and pick your perfect time to play. Call in advance to confirm availability.
  3. Show Up & Show Off: Head out to your local Bowlero, present your voucher, and you are all set for the ultimate fun!

Don’t let the fun expire! Please note - your offer is valid until June, 25 2026. Promotional value must be used by this date.
